iJustDoit is a simple to do list application. You can use it to manage your to do lists.

Right Now it does following things:

1. Create new tasks
2. Categorize to dos
3. Mark Tasks as done! and some others


Next phase will include functionality for 

1. Email reminders for upcoming tasks
2. More customization of tasks
3. Creating subtasks for tasks and few other

If you have any questions regarding this app pl send me an email at: atul.veer@gmail.com
